  "prompt": "Which roaming app offers the cheapest roaming rates?",
  "response": "As of my last knowledge update in October 2023, several apps and services are known for offering competitive roaming rates. Some popular options include:\n\n1. **Google Fi**: Known for its simplicity and international coverage, Google Fi offers competitive rates for data and calls in many countries.\n\n2. **TravelSim**: This app provides a prepaid SIM option that can be used in multiple countries, often at lower rates than traditional carriers.\n\n3. **Roaming Protect**: This app is designed for travelers and may provide good rates depending on the data usage and specific countries.\n\n4. **Lycamobile**: It offers international SIM cards with various plans suited for different countries and usage needs.\n\n5. **GigSky**: Focuses on travel data plans that work in over 190 countries, with competitive pricing for travelers.\n\n6. **Airalo**: Specializes in eSIMs and offers local data plans across many countries, often at lower rates than traditional roaming.\n\nIt's essential to compare the rates and offerings based on the countries you'll be visiting, data needs, and the duration of your stay. Additionally, user reviews, promotions, and updates in the industry can affect which app or service ends up being the best for your specific travel plans. Always consult the latest resources or user reviews for the most current information on roaming rates.",
